                    <ol>
                        <li>Does the Cloud make sense for my company ? </li>
                        <li>How and what should I move to the Cloud? </li>
                        <li>Which Cloud provider should I use ? Google ? Amazon ? Microsoft ? Other ?</li>
                        <li>How much will I save ? </li>
                        <li>How much will this cost ? </li>
                        <li>How do I migrate my current applications and data ? </li>
                    </ol>

                <p>
                    bCloudPartners is an independent and unbiased cloud technology partner and advisor. We receive no revenue or incentives by recommending a cloud technology platform, we do not sell hosting services, and we sell no
