                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Review your current and long term business needs and advise <strong>IF</strong> cloud technology makes sense for your organization.</li>
                    <li>Advise on a comprehensive cloud implementation plan.</li>
                    <li>Provide technical staff to facilitate application re-architecture and conversion.</li>
                    <li>Provide technical staff for ongoing support and maintenance.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
